name: Medina Heat
description: Everything worth remembering in Medina happened in the bloated hours of Tisbaar. These were the hottest hours of any day, with a sun that took up so much of the sky you couldn't look up in any direction. Tisbaar was also the only window when spirits and souls in transition could move about town. Townspeople stayed in doors out of respect, whispering whatever needed to be said. Time crawled and smelt of sleep.
